{"tid":2444803,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國法院裁定，暫停執行對小米的投資禁令","createTime":"2021-03-13T06:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T03:53:44.000Z","uid":303304,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dda1b87999737012b2944c63b8538b699505c509","tid":2444803,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:22:07.000Z","msg":"美國法院裁定，暫停執行對小米(<a href=\"http://01810.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01810.HK&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=2b2593c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01810.HK</a>)的投資禁令。 美國上屆特朗普政府於任內最後一日，將小米及多間中資公司納入與中國軍方相關名單當中，觸發金融機構需要出售相關投資，有關法令原訂於下周起生效。 法官Rudolph Contreras表示，法院認定沒有給出令人信服的解釋，說明國家安全利益面臨重大風險。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%8D%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3-01810-hk-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4-034029316.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%259F%25B7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B1%25B3-01810-hk-%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BB%25A4-034029316.html&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=fb5fd0cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%8D%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3-01810-hk-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4-034029316.html</a>"},{"pid":"0c33017bdb5a566518df831302c49ae1da2c1f81","tid":2444803,"uid":303304,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:22:15.000Z","msg":"小米表示，歡迎有關裁決，認為美方指控是武斷且不可靠。"},{"pid":"9ea562080af428f12e2c04249aad66bdd295f4cd","tid":2444803,"uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T06:22:41.000Z","msg":